content:
The Mid-Term Adjustments Lightning web component gives insurance carrier administrators a straightforward way to:

Enroll new hires in the middle of a contract term.

Terminate policies at any time.

Upload New Hire Census Data for Enrollment: After a contract is in place, upload group benefits product enrollment data with new hire census members and dependents.

Terminate a Policy for a Single Member: Terminate policies of primary members and associated dependents individually in the middle of a contract. Get notified when the termination is completed and receive a list of errors if termination couldn't be completed.

Terminate Member Policies in Bulk: Terminate policies of the primary members and dependents in bulk in the middle of a contract.
title: Group Benefits Enrollment and Termination Workflows
